videos.description: West Virginia's Sagaba Konate changes direction mid shot and nails the finger roll in the first half.
videos.headline: Konate converts on the finger roll

videos.description: After poking the ball loose, West Virginia's Jevon Carter grabs the steal and throws down the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Carter's steal sets up two-handed slam

videos.description: Fordham's Will Tavares tries taking it to the paint but is blocked by West Virginia's Sagaba Konate in the first half.
videos.headline: Konate rejects Tavares

videos.description: West Virginia's Sagaba Konate hauls in the offensive rebound and puts up the contested layup for an and-1 opportunity.
videos.headline: Konate converts putback for and-1 chance

videos.description: Fordham's Joseph Chartouny tries going up with the layup but is rejected by West Virginia's Wesley Harris in the second half.
videos.headline: Harris denies Chartouny's layup

videos.description: Fordham's Joseph Chartouny attempts to take it to the paint for a layup but is denied by West Virginia's Sagaba Konate.
videos.headline: Konate stuffs Chartouny

videos.description: West Virginia's Teddy Allen kicks the ball out to Daxter Miles Jr. for the 3-pointer in the second half.
videos.headline: Allen finds Miles open from downtown

videos.description: Fordham's Cavit Havsa gets the steal and finds Will Tavares in transition for the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Havsa's steal sets up Tavares' slam

videos.description: West Virginia's Chase Harler dishes it to Daxter Miles Jr. behind the arc for the long 3-pointer in the second half.
videos.headline: Miles knocks down long 3-pointer

videos.description: West Virginia's Daxter Miles Jr. sets up Lamont West in the post for the two-handed dunk in the second half.
videos.headline: West throws down two-handed slam

videos.description: West Virginia's Daxter Miles JR. finds Sagaba Konate down low for the loud two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Konate finishes emphatic dunk for and-1 chance
